            <div class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ã‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠:</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">{{ $order->items_count }} ‡∏ä‡∏¥‡πâ‡∏ô</div>
        </div>
        
